OL,3,CTrump says he will take legal action
OL,4,Cagainst the BBC over edited speech
OL,6,FDonald Trump says he will sue the BBC
OL,7,Fnext week after the corporation
OL,8,Fapologised but declined to compensate
OL,9,Fhim for its edited version of a 2021
OL,10,Fspeech broadcast by Panorama.
OL,12,FSpeaking to reporters on board Air
OL,13,FForce One on Friday, Mr Trump said:
OL,14,F"We'll sue them for anywhere between 1
OL,15,Fbillion dollars (#759.8 million) and 5
OL,16,Fbillion dollars (#3.79 billion),
OL,17,Fprobably sometime next week."
OL,19,FThe BBC apologised but said it refused
OL,20,Fto pay financial compensation.
