OL,6,FThe corporation said the splicing of
OL,7,Fthe speech was an "error of judgment".
OL,9,FStill, it rejected his compensation
OL,10,Fdemands, after Mr Trump's lawyers
OL,11,Fthreatened to sue the BBC for one
OL,12,Fbillion dollars in damages unless a
OL,13,Fretraction and apology were published.
OL,15,FMr Trump's lawyers had given the BBC a
OL,16,F10pm Friday deadline to respond.
