OL,6,FEarlier in the week, Mr Trump said in
OL,7,Fan interview with Fox News that the
OL,8,FBBC had "defrauded the public" over
OL,9,Fthe edit, which made it appear as if
OL,10,Fhe was explicitly urging people to
OL,11,Fattack the US Capitol on January 6
OL,12,F2021.
OL,14,FSeparately, Mr Trump told GB News in
OL,15,Fan interview broadcast on Saturday he
OL,16,Ffelt an "obligation" to take legal
OL,17,Faction against the public broadcaster.
OL,19,F"I'm not looking to get into lawsuits,
OL,20,Fbut I think I have an obligation to do
OL,21,Fit," he said.
