OL,6,F"This was so egregious. If you don't
OL,7,Fdo it, you don't stop it from
OL,8,Fhappening again with other people."
OL,10,FChairman Samir Shah has sent a
OL,11,Fpersonal letter to the White House to
OL,12,Fapologise for the editing, and lawyers
OL,13,Ffor the corporation have written to
OL,14,Fthe president's legal team, a BBC
