OL,6,FThe programme, broadcast a week before
OL,7,Fthe 2024 US election results, spliced
OL,8,Ftwo clips together so that Mr Trump
OL,9,Fappeared to tell the crowd: "We're
OL,10,Fgoing to walk down to the Capitol...
OL,11,Fand I'll be there with you. And we
OL,12,Ffight. We fight like hell."
OL,14,FOn board Air Force One, Mr Trump told
OL,15,Fthe Daily Telegraph Prime Minister Sir
OL,16,FKeir Starmer was "very embarrassed" by
OL,17,Fthe incident and said he would speak
OL,18,Fwith him over the weekend.
